name: "Bubble Bath" by Sunny Crittenden
description:
"Bubble Bath" is the vanilla companion piece to "Bathing In The Blood Of My Enemies". Both were originally drawn as a colouring page for Sunny's Patreon and coloured separately by Sunny to illustrate how versatile each page really is.

"Bubble Bath" features a brown girl with green eyes and black hair with magenta highlights, relaxing in a nice blue bath tub full of bubbles. The wallpaper in the bathroom is pink and features skulls and purple flowers. The piece is about the concept of partaking in self-care for good mental health.
